These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different games are played: billiard, bridge, canasta
1. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Game   | bridge | canasta | billiard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, airplane, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Transport   | trike | airplane | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, musician, engineer
1. the accountant is on the far left##1
2. the engineer is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Job   | accountant | musician | engineer |

